{"tid":1512972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣做錯曬方向！！！ 唔該大家入嚟睇","createTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:00:07.000Z","uid":272538,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d34da89f509deddb594e45b604120fb373283175","tid":1512972,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"開隔離台，朱凱迪新髮型都多人關心過呢篇文<br />\n我最後一次開呢個post， 如果都係冇人關心嘅話，我唔會再post。<br />\n比較長，下面有少少分析，希望大家睇曬佢。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話之前嘅文宣冇用，但係好多文宣都唔係比俾政治冷感又或者係淺藍嘅人士睇，而係俾已經「想關心」嘅人睇。<br />\n<br />\n喺網上同人罵戰左兩個月同埋落區做過文宣工作後， 就知道其實網上面出聲嘅好多都係假account，又或者根本唔係生活緊喺香港嘅人。與其花咁多時間同呢啲人理論，不如我哋落區，同返<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係住喺香港嘅人對話</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n喺我同朋友最近落區嘅工作入面（ 包括荃灣觀塘深水埗黃大仙黃埔中環，再早啲之前都去過北角，不過北角係另一回事），發現香港人嘅比率係咁：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">1. 不能溝通+比「暴徒」更暴力類型</span></span> - 一講有集會/示威就已經發脾氣，不可理喻，拒絕傾偈，屌左你先，叫你去死<br />\n比率：100個入面先有2個，2%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 被害妄想症類型</span></span> - 話你派生理鹽水=威脅佢哋安全<br />\n比率：100個入面先有1個，1%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">3. 漠不關己+無睇新聞類型</span></span> - 「唔出街咪無事囉」， 「民居點會有事呀」，覺得件事仲係離自己好遠<br />\n比率：100個入面有25個，25%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">4. 漠不關己但貪小便宜類型</span></span> - 都唔係好關自己事㗎，不過有免費野，攞咗先<br />\n比率：100個入面有15個，15%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">5. 明白類型</span></span> - 知道發生緊咩事<br />\n比率：100個入面有15個，15%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">6. 加油打氣類</span></span> - 叫你萬事小心<br />\n比率：100個入面有10個，10%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">7. 送錢送物資類型</span></span> - 知道發生緊咩事，叫你加油， 轉個頭送支嘢飲畀你，或者想捐錢<br />\n比率：100個入面有2個，2%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">8. 比你走得更前類型</span></span> - 接到之後，多謝你， 話自己已經有，叫你留番畀有需要嘅人<br />\n比率：100個入面有5個，5%<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">9. 對人類沒有信心類型</span></span> - 唔相信有免費物資，唔相信有人會對自己好，唔信有咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳<br />\n比率：淨番落黎嘅25%<br />\n<br />\n如圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a6QfjCq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa6QfjCq.jpg&h=bd6f9818&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本上1同2，我哋可以完全放棄，其實亦比我哋想像中少。 大家覺得好多係因為大家focus咗喺網上面，佢哋亦都係做緊鍵盤戰士，營做有好多人嘅假象，去到現實其實咁都冇咁多（你睇撐警大會都知...）。 或者藍絲要勇武/鬧出聲其實都唔係咁容易，都需要勇氣，肯做嘅人其實唔多。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我哋落區要做嘅就係主攻3、4同埋9， 佢哋佔左65%呀！！！！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span> 呢一班人冇乜態度冇乜感覺，唔踩到上心口都唔知道痛。<br />\n<br />\n呢場運動要贏，唔係靠網上鍵盤攻擊，而係要啲人行出嚟，實實在在咁去做事。唔理係做前線，定係去圍管理處要求交代，都係需要人。<br />\n我哋要將呢一場運動拉返落去佢哋嗰度，話畀佢哋聽警察放催淚彈放山埃係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔會理</span></strong></span>居民嘅健康後果！！！<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">得我地在乎！！！！！！！！ 得我哋唔計較咁付出！！！！！！！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n從來改變人嘅都係因為愛，而唔係因為對罵。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">就算唔將佢哋變成黃色，至少要令佢哋變白色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n立即加入落區派文宣禮品包（生理鹽水/口罩）小組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NPHXlxSUPbx3KLg6oV8pjQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNPHXlxSUPbx3KLg6oV8pjQ&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=fe7f4e22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NPHXlxSUPbx3KLg6oV8pjQ</a>"},{"pid":"e449c5f9cd6467371ff10b248bb9e95375404033","tid":1512972,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etSapPa.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetSapPa.gif&h=0cba6709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=c3084248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=aa0817e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=5d08fa21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"4363ffebd784542e093664d5f06d01ca10cefa3b","tid":1512972,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">今晚見</div></span></span><br />\n