7523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:11:44.000Z","msg":"支持！！push！"},{"pid":"06b6d8f87f48bf1ae4c4c57a1c9c4eec694c7950","tid":1512972,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:38:53.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"5f90f250aa0a9e07a8b66fcddac3f185638ac0e5","tid":1512972,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:06:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好失望"},{"pid":"5aabd01e9a2e6a690082a2f58f3932cbdf74f04c","tid":1512972,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:45:03.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打落區調查 數據有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac50b7e04ef07fd3ade884e62da49499a246261e","tid":1512972,"uid":272538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T00:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8048b472d028cfc96d92300eb3d81860c7a8c9a","tid":1512972,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T13:00:07.000Z","msg":"記住，想擴大文宣威力、脫離同溫層，<br />\n要擴大文宣既可能性，<br />\n中立淺藍只會自私地關心自己既衣食住行<br />\n<br />\n文宣方向：<br />\n- 放大緊急法既生活影響<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFkrSTk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFkrSTk.jpg&h=19ae1df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/snwVMdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsnwVMdn.jpg&h=58d66585&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大林鄭既攬炒慾望<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WT8dxUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWT8dxUs.jpg&h=d3e77a04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asdJaF8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasdJaF8.jpg&h=996481da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHbe1NO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHbe1NO.jpg&h=a377df13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 一人一個淺黃、中立既經濟行動<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YtJaKn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YtJaKn.jpg&h=c45f7608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0nRnrhK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0nRnrhK.jpg&h=b96ff78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DK00cXM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDK00cXM.jpg&h=2a6e1403&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 放大tg既害處，影響飲食<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKrq8t1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKrq8t1.jpg&h=91688cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2pwjAH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2pwjAH.jpg&h=0cc41943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piePQHo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiePQHo.jpg&h=c4afef69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- keep住loop 721同白色恐怖，影響外出<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cw50cWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCw50cWL.jpg&h=59d05248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LS7JU96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLS7JU96.jpg&h=40e97624&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gosaz97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGosaz97.jpg&h=7636c5c2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}